&lt;OPINION&gt;<br>
Personally I kinda wished some of the bigger mob intentions carried some weight.  Sure, I agree that intentions on bosses that take one group doesn't make sense.  But ones like Master Yael or CoM that require more than one group(leading to public signups for smallish guilds) leads to some pretty heavy organizational effort.  It'd be a shame to waste 1-3 days getting people to sign up and find out &lt;Uber Guild&gt; decided it was their day that day.  <br>
<br>
